      834,
      512
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "C $P(A) = P(\\bar{B}) \\cdot P(A|\\bar{B}) - P(B) \\cdot P(A|B)$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      188,
      512,
      834,
      556
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "D $P(A) = P(B) \\cdot P(A|B) + P(\\bar{B}) \\cdot P(A|\\bar{B})$."
